<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-navy-950">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">About Us</h2>
      <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-gold-500 mx-auto"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          At Sandycove School of Music, we believe in providing tailored, effective tutoring to help every student reach their full potential. Whether you're a complete beginner or preparing for grade exams, our approach is personalised to your goals and learning style.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Our teachers hold a BA in Music and bring over 25 years of combined teaching experience. We specialise in piano tuition across classical, jazz, contemporary, and pop styles, preparing students for RIAM, ABRSM, and Trinity College London examinations.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Located in the heart of Dun Laoghaire, we offer a welcoming and supportive environment where students of all ages and abilities can develop their musical skills and confidence.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-xl bg-navy-800 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center p-8">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto text-gold-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 19V6l12-3v13M9 19c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zm12-3c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zM9 10l12-3" />
            </svg>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">25+ years combined teaching experience</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
